parameters:
\bustMsgExp[2, 1]\nc<Senpai>"Dear customer, I apologize, but we do not offer such a
course. You will be charged four times the standard amount."
\nc<Customer>"Huh? Four times?! Are you kidding me?"

\nc<Senpai>"If you are unable to pay, then as per our policy, we have
no choice but to add you to the blacklist."

\nc<Customer>"Hey now, there are other succubus businesses out there,
you've got some nerve..."

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>"Oh? Even among succubus businesses, blacklists are shared,
you know? If you get blacklisted here, you won't be able to
use other places either."

\nc<Customer>"Damn it... Fine. I had a great time thanks to you this
time... So it's four times the amount, right?"

\nc<Senpai>"How magnanimous of you. Thank you for your payment. We look
forward to your next visit."

\nc<Saki>"Senpai, are you going to let him off? Wouldn't it be better
to just put him on the blacklist..."
\nc<Senpai>"If we do that and he goes somewhere else, it's all over."

\nc<Senpai>"That person just broke a little rule and paid four times
the amount. We can't let such easy prey get snatched away by
others."

\bustMsgExp[1, 1]\nc<Saki>"What? If you're registered on the blacklist, you can't go
to other places..."

\bustMsgExp[2, 0]\nc<Senpai>"Succubus businesses don't get along, so there's no way they
share blacklists. They're all in competition for customers."

\bustMsgExp[1, 2]\nc<Saki>"I can never tell when you're lying, Senpai. You say it so
calmly without changing your expression..."
\nc<Senpai>"Hehe, I'll take that as a compliment."

\nc<Senpai>"Good work, Saki. Maybe we should officially introduce a
soap course using the shower booths next time?"
\nc<>Saki trudges off to prepare to go home...
